These are Puzzles for 4x4 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-2-1::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: adventure, comedy, fantasy, mystery
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: metal, r&b, salsa, techno
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: davidoff, chaman, old-henry, siglo
The people have 4 different jobs:  pilot, librarian, designer, entrepreneur
1. the chaman-smoker is the fan of techno##1
2. the old-henry-smoker is between the person watching fantasy movies and the person watching mystery movies##2
3. the chaman-smoker is the pilot##1
4. the entrepreneur is on the left of the pilot##1
5. the fan of metal is on the left of the davidoff-smoker##1
6. the designer is the person watching fantasy movies##1
7. the fan of r&b is on the left of the person watching mystery movies##1
8. the davidoff-smoker is on the far right##1
9. the person watching comedy movies is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2     |     3      |    4     |
| Movie-Genre   | comedy | mystery   | adventure  | fantasy  |
| Music-Genre   | r&b    | techno    | metal      | salsa    |
| Cigar   | siglo | chaman | old-henry | davidoff |
| Job     | entrepreneur  | pilot       | librarian    | designer     |

