.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-2-2::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: cooking, drawing, singing, woodworking
There are 4 different favourite colors: orange, white, fuchsia, lilac
4 different pets are kept: bird, dog, frog, lizard
The people have 4 different jobs:  security-guard, teacher, software-developer, musician
1. the musician is on the right of the person who's hobby is woodworking##1
2. the person who's hobby is cooking is on the far right##1
3. the owner of the lizard is the teacher##1
4. the person who's hobby is singing is on the right of the person who's hobby is drawing##1
5. the person who likes lilac is between the owner of the frog and the security-guard##2
6. the musician is between the person who likes lilac and the owner of the lizard##2
7. the owner of the bird is on the far right##1
8. the person who likes white is on the left of the person who's hobby is singing##1
9. the person who likes fuchsia is on the right of the owner of the dog##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2      |    3     |     4      |
| Hobby         | woodworking | drawing    | singing  | cooking    |
| Color   | orange      | white  | lilac  | fuchsia |
| Pet           | lizard      | frog       | dog      | bird       |
| Job         | teacher    | musician | software-developer | security-guard |

