.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-2-3::.
There 4 different types of food: artichoke, blueberry, lemon, mango
4 different pets are kept: guinea-pig, bird, cat, hedgehog
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: rowing, soccer, skiing, volleyball
The people use 4 different means of transport: helicopter, motorbike, roller, subway
1. the person who's sport is skiing is the person driving the motorbike##1
2. the person driving the motorbike is on the left of the person who's sport is volleyball##1
3. the person driving the roller is on the left of the person driving the motorbike##1
4. the person driving the motorbike is on the left of the person driving the helicopter##1
5. the person eating lemon is on the left of the owner of the cat##1
6. the person who's sport is soccer is the owner of the hedgehog##1
7. the person eating mango is on the right of the owner of the cat##1
8. the person eating artichoke is between the owner of the guinea-pig and the owner of the hedgehog##2
9. the owner of the cat is between the person eating lemon and the person who's sport is soccer##2

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1     |     2     |      3      |     4     |
| Food        | blueberry | lemon     | artichoke   | mango     |
| Pet       | bird   | guinea-pig   | cat | hedgehog |
| Sport         | rowing   | skiing | volleyball       | soccer    |
| Transport   | roller    | motorbike | helicopter  | subway    |

