4 different pets are kept: bird, frog, hamster, pony
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: aconite, dahlia, zinnia, lily
 1. the person who's birthday is in december is on the far right##1
 2. the person who's birthday is in march is the fisherman##1
 3. the owner of the bird is on the right of the person who growslily##1
 4. the person who growsaconite is on the far left##1
 5. the person who's birthday is in march is the owner of the frog##1
 6. the owner of the pony is on the right of the person who growsaconite##1
 7. the person who's birthday is in december is the police-officer##1
 8. the person who's birthday is in july is on the right of the person who's birthday is in march##1
 9. the fisherman is on the left of the person who growsdahlia##1
10. the mechanic is between the owner of the bird and the teacher##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2    |      3       |       4        |
| Job           | fisherman  | teacher | mechanic     | police-officer |
