.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-2-5::.
There are 4 different favourite colors: chestnut, mauve, coral, amber
The people have 4 different jobs:  freelancer, lawyer, security-guard, social-worker
City: san-francisco, hannover, venice, boston
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: basketball, ice-hockey, sailing, weightlifting
 1. the person who likes coral is on the right of the person who likes mauve##1
 2. the person who's sport is basketball is on the far left##1
 3. the security-guard is the person who likes mauve##1
 4. the security-guard is on the left of the person who's sport is sailing##1
 5. the person traveling to boston is on the left of the person who likes amber##1
 6. the person who likes coral is on the left of the person traveling to boston##1
 7. the social-worker is on the left of the person who likes chestnut##1
 8. the lawyer is the person traveling to hannover##1
 9. the person who likes coral is between the person who's sport is weightlifting and the person traveling to san-francisco##2
10. the person traveling to venice is the person who's sport is sailing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1        |       2       |       3       |     4      |
| Color          | mauve         | coral         | chestnut     | amber      |
| Job           | security-guard | social-worker | freelancer    | lawyer     |
| City   | san-francisco      | venice       | boston    | hannover       |
| Sport         | basketball     | sailing       | weightlifting | ice-hockey |

