.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-2-6::.
4 different games are played: snooker, chess, backgammon, scrabble
There are 4 different favourite beverages: almond-milk, sprite, hot-chocolate, iced-tea
There are 4 different nationalities: chinese, dutch, polish, turkish
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: climbing, cricket, cycling, sailing
1. the person drinking almond-milk is between the person who's sport is sailing and the person drinking hot-chocolate##2
2. the person playing chess is between the person drinking almond-milk and the turkish##2
3. the polish is between the person who's sport is cricket and the dutch##2
4. the person playing backgammon is on the left of the dutch##1
5. the polish is the polish##1
6. the dutch is on the right of the person who's sport is cycling##1
7. the dutch is on the left of the person playing snooker##1
8. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the far right##1
9. the person drinking sprite is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2      |    3     |     4     |
| Game           | backgammon | chess | snooker  | scrabble |
| Beverage   | sprite      | iced-tea       | almond-milk     | hot-chocolate      |
| Nationality   | turkish   | dutch      | polish   | chinese   |
| Sport         | cycling   | sailing    | climbing | cricket   |

