 4. the fan of metal is the person who growsmarigold##1
 5. the russian is on the left of the person playing scrabble##1
 6. the person playing chess is on the left of the person who growssunflower##1
 7. the argentine is the person who growsrose##1
 8. the fan of soul is on the far right##1
 9. the person playing chess is on the right of the person playing go##1
10. the dutch is the person who growsmarigold##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2    |    3    |    4    |
| Game   | go | chess | poker  | scrabble  |
| Music-Genre   | blues       | metal   | dubstep | soul    |
| Nationality   | argentine   | dutch   | russian | british |
