3. the person traveling to hamburg is on the left of the person traveling to prague##1
4. the person driving the car is on the left of the person who's hobby is hiking##1
5. the person driving the jet-ski is between the person driving the quad-bike and the person watching documentary movies##2
6. the person who's hobby is photography is the person watching zombie movies##1
7. the person who's hobby is collecting is on the left of the person traveling to san-francisco##1
8. the person who's hobby is card-games is on the left of the person who's hobby is hiking##1

.:: Answer ::.
